  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>A thin tensile metal blade, light in weight but long in reach designed for quick darting attacks to target weak points in enemy defenses with lightning swiftness.</em></p>\n<p>Deals piercing damage equal to 1d6(1d8) + your Strength or Dexterity modifier.</p>\n<p><strong>Special.</strong> If you wield a rapier in one hand and don't have a weapon or shield in your other hand, the rapier deals 1d8 damage instead of 1d6. </p>\n<p><strong>Finesse. </strong>When making an attack with a finesse weapon, you use your choice of your Strength or Dexterity modifier for the attack and damage rolls. You must use the same modifier for both rolls.</p>",
